root: ^This looks really stable! Gotta pat myself on the back for this one.
^One of the planks had loosened and fallen off when I visited once.
^Being the kid I was, always looking for new ways to play, I seized the opportunity and
^used the remaining plank as a monkey bar and swung myself back and forth in the newly made gap.
^I miss those simple days of being allowed to just be a kid. They didn’t last long…
